# .NET Code Review — /dotnet-review

## Trigger

```
/dotnet-review <file-or-folder>
/dotnet-review                     ← file đang active trong context
/dotnet-review <file> --quick      ← chỉ blocking issues
/dotnet-review <file> --security   ← tập trung security & data leakage
```

---

## Bước 1 — Load context

Đọc (nếu có): `docs/project_overview.md` → architecture, naming  
Skill `10_sk_dotnet_impl.mdc` và `11_sk_dotnet_review.mdc` tự load khi file `.cs` mở.

---

## Bước 2 — Chạy 10 lenses

| # | Lens | Focus chính |
|---|------|------------|
| L1 | Async Correctness | `.Result`/`.Wait()`, `async void`, CT propagation |
| L2 | EF Core Safety | N+1, `AsNoTracking`, unbounded query, full entity load |
| L3 | DI Lifetime | Scoped→Singleton, service locator, BackgroundService |
| L4 | Exception Handling | Silent swallow, `throw ex;`, PG error discrimination |
| L5 | Security & Data Leakage | SQL injection, PII in log, cross-tenant StoreId |
| L6 | Resource Management | `new HttpClient()`, `IDisposable`, transaction rollback |
| L7 | Performance | StringBuilder, early materialization, `Any()` vs `Count()` |
| L8 | Domain Model | `public set`, anemic model, invariant |
| L9 | Observability | Structured log, OTel span, log level, stack trace |
| L10 | .NET 6 Compat | Primary ctor, FrozenDictionary, Polly v8 syntax |

Severity: **🔴 BLOCK** (fix trước merge) · **🟡 WARN** (nên fix) · **🔵 NOTE** (optional)

`--quick` mode: chỉ L1, L2, L3, L4, L5, L10  
`--security` mode: L5 deep-dive, + L1, L4, L10

---

## Bước 3 — Output format

Lưu vào `.ai/reviews/DOTNET-REVIEW-[filename]-[DATE].md`:

```
# .NET Code Review — [FileName]
> Stack: .NET 6 · EF Core 6 · Polly v7

## Verdict
🔴 Blocking: N | 🟡 Warning: N | 🔵 Note: N
Overall: ✅ APPROVED / ⚠️ NEEDS FIX / 🔴 BLOCKED

## 🔴 Blocking Issues
### BLOCK-01: [Title]
- Lens: [L#]  File: `path/file.cs` (line ~N)
- Found:   [problematic snippet]
- Problem: [tại sao đây là vấn đề]
- Impact:  [hậu quả: crash / data loss / security breach]
- Fix:     [corrected snippet]

## 🟡 Warnings
### WARN-01: [Title]
- Lens/File/Found/Problem/Risk/Suggestion

## 🔵 Notes
### NOTE-01: [one-liner suggestion]

## ✅ Good Patterns
- [ClassName.Method]: [tại sao tốt]

## 📋 Fix Checklist
- [ ] BLOCK-01 / - [ ] WARN-01 (optional)
```

In chat summary:
```
🔍 .NET Review: [FileName]
🔴 Blocking: N | 🟡 Warning: N | 🔵 Note: N
Verdict: [APPROVED/NEEDS FIX/BLOCKED]
Saved: .ai/reviews/DOTNET-REVIEW-[name]-[DATE].md

  fix BLOCK-01 now     → Claude fix trực tiếp
  /fix-task BLOCK-01   → Tạo task file cho Cursor
  accept warnings      → Log TODO, proceed to merge
```

---

## Behavior Rules

1. Không bịa issue — chỉ report những gì thực sự thấy. Nếu lens không có issue → ghi `✅ No issues`.
2. Fix snippet phải compilable .NET 6 / C# 10 — không dùng API từ .NET 7+.
3. `--quick` — chỉ BLOCK issues + tổng WARN count, không detail WARN.
4. F&B domain: throughput (1000+ req/s), multi-tenant (StoreId isolation), tiền tệ dùng `decimal`.

