## Top Anti-patterns tại Dcorp

| Anti-pattern | Lens | Severity |
|---|---|---|
| `new HttpClient()` trong service | L6 | 🔴 BLOCK |
| N+1 trong report generation | L2 | 🔴 BLOCK |
| Log PII (Phone, CardNumber, OTP) | L5 | 🔴 BLOCK |
| Scoped DbContext inject vào Singleton | L3 | 🔴 BLOCK |
| Thiếu StoreId filter → cross-tenant leak | L5 | 🔴 BLOCK |
| `float`/`double` cho tiền tệ | L7 | 🔴 BLOCK |
| Primary constructor C# 12 trong .NET 6 | L10 | 🔴 BLOCK |
| `catch (Exception) { return null; }` | L4 | 🔴 BLOCK |
| Thiếu `AsNoTracking()` trên list query | L2 | 🟡 WARN |
| `throw ex;` thay vì `throw;` | L4 | 🟡 WARN |
| Thiếu CancellationToken propagation | L1 | 🟡 WARN |
| `AddResilienceHandler` (Polly v8) | L10 | 🔴 BLOCK |
